FT  24 SEP 94 / Survey of Residential Property (8): Hostel takeovers
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Freehold pubs on offer from Business Sales Group (071-439 6617) range from
the Horse and Groom at Caulcott near the Oxford Canal in Oxfordshire for
Pounds 97,500 (which takes Pounds 1,700 a week net of VAT, split evenly
between wet and dry sales) to the Horse and Groom at Upper Oddington near
Stow-on-the-Wold in the Cotswolds for Pounds 435,000, which brings a
cottage, 2.25 acres including a stream and trout pond, and seven en-suite
letting bedrooms (producing about 20 per cent of the Pounds 250,000 net
