the year to August 1993), for Pounds 295,000, down from Pounds 320,000. Also
reduced are the New Inn in Priddy near Wells 'popular with cavers and
walkers' (Pounds 445,000, from Pounds 475,000), and the Tower Inn at Slapton
in Devon, now Pounds 299,950 from Pounds 400,000.
